rankingCodAns.title: Ranking de Cód. ANS
rankingCodAns.sql: With CTE As ( Select `Glosa Item - Cód. ANS`, Count(*) As Qtd From KORA Group By `Glosa Item - Cód. ANS` ) Select CTE.*, Concat(Round(Qtd * 100.0 / (Select Sum(Qtd) From CTE),2), '%') As Percentual From CTE Order By 2 Desc
